    <h2>Professional Summary</h2>
    <p>Healthcare has been the focus of my career for more than 15 years. Throughout that time, I've partnered with physicians, healthcare organizations, and veterinary practices to improve patient care, operational efficiency, and business performance through laboratory diagnostics, specialty diagnostics, healthcare technology, software, and capital equipment. I believe the best sales professionals become trusted advisors rather than simply product representatives — understanding each customer's business, identifying opportunities for improvement, and delivering solutions that create measurable value.</p>
    <p>My experience spans laboratory diagnostics, specialty diagnostics, point-of-care diagnostics, toxicology, healthcare technology, practice management software, capital equipment, pharmaceuticals, vaccines, and medical devices.</p>

    <h2>Career Highlights</h2>
    <div class="highlight-box">
      <ul>
        <li>Increased Quest Diagnostics specialty toxicology utilization from approximately 3,000 to more than 13,000 tests per week</li>
        <li>Promoted into Quest Diagnostics' Specialty Sales organization after one year through a competitive interview process</li>
        <li>Selected as one of only three representatives nationwide to serve on the Quest Diagnostics Commercial Advisory Committee</li>
        <li>Served as one of only two Florida Prescription Drug Monitoring Specialists</li>
        <li>Managed a $9.2 million healthcare territory serving approximately 160 veterinary hospitals</li>
        <li>Achieved 238% of annual new business quota at Labcorp</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

